This page on SteamDB showcases a curated list of games tagged as 'MOBA' (Multiplayer Online Battle Arena). MOBA is a popular genre within the gaming community on Steam, where players engage in competitive team-based gameplay in real-time. Developers and Steam users apply this tag to games that feature strategic teamwork, distinct hero roles, and continuous action. Players assume the control of a champion or hero, working cooperatively with their teammates to destroy the enemy's base while defending their own. The dynamic nature of these games demands quick adaptation and strategic thinking, making them a favorite choice for both casual and competitive gamers.
